<HEADLINE>
FT  16 DEC 93 / UK Company News: Dickie
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The directors of James Dickie said they were not aware of the reason for the
sharp improvement in the company's share price. Shares in the USM-quoted
manufacturer of engineering components rose 9p to 90p on Tuesday and a
further 5p to 95p yesterday.
