enabled the group to swing from operating losses before non-recurring items
of Pounds 680,000 to profits of Pounds 135,000 for the full year.
Turnover slipped to Pounds 6.9m (Pounds 8.53m) of which Pounds 402,000
(Pounds 1.42m) arose from discontinued operations. Losses per share emerged
at 16.82p (20.77p).
